{"id":151722,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/哈西德派报纸ps掉照片中的女性/","date":"2011-05-11T16:30:44Z","modified":"2011-05-11T16:30:44Z","title":"哈西德派报纸PS掉照片中的女性","content":"<p>五月一日，美国特种部队发动了追捕本拉登的突袭行动。白宫当天在其Flickr官方主页公布了一幅著名的照片，展现总统、副总统、国务卿等高级官员在焦急的观看追捕行动的画面。这幅照片被媒体广为引用，仅仅Flickr页面的浏览量就超过240万。一家哈西德派报纸Der Tzitung也转载了照片，但有意思的是它PS掉了画面中的两位女性，其中一位是国务卿希拉里克林顿。哈西德派是犹太教正统派的一个分支，它从照片删除女性的理由或者是性暗示，或者是被认为展现了男性和女性之间不恰当的互动。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14b8b50c/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%93%88%E8%A5%BF%E5%BE%B7%E6%B4%BE%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B8PS%E6%8E%89%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F10%2F1048222%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%93%88%E8%A5%BF%E5%BE%B7%E6%B4%BE%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B8PS%E6%8E%89%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F10%2F1048222%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091877386/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14b8b50c/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091877386/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14b8b50c/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=7c4bnWzFVzg:tAHiFecBAXQ:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=7c4bnWzFVzg:tAHiFecBAXQ:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</di